{"tid":2216941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"再有終院法官退任：海外法官或總辭","createTime":"2020-09-25T05:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T08:03:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"42edc12378da4482ae4fdfe8ab3726b40e66c4b3","tid":2216941,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:42:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/T3JWXRP3UNCYPGVDM7DPR72CM4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FT3JWXRP3UNCYPGVDM7DPR72CM4%2F&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheOaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=8d8d2586\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FT3JWXRP3UNCYPGVDM7DPR72CM4%2F&h=cad1ae63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/T3JWXRP3UNCYPGVDM7DPR72CM4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n再有終院法官退任：海外法官或總辭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VHhiUn2KmZRn4RwegRYK8PBKRSY=/720x525/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FTH5A6Q4BVFYJMXPQ653HEEQZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVHhiUn2KmZRn4RwegRYK8PBKRSY%3D%2F720x525%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFTH5A6Q4BVFYJMXPQ653HEEQZE.jpg&h=7db493a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n終院非常任法官苗禮治<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】終審法院繼非常任法官施覺民（James Spigelman）在本月初，據稱因港版國安法而辭職後，有傳媒報道另一非常任法官苗禮治亦以身體不宜長途旅程為由，不再來港審案。苗禮治接受傳媒查詢時承認，確有全體海外法官請辭的可能，但希望不會發生。<br />\n<br />\n現年88歲的英國前上訴法院常任高級法官苗禮治勳爵向《明報》透露，他2018年獲延任時，已表示身體狀况未必適宜長途旅程，不再來港審案，並表示自己兩年前已從終院退休。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n司法機構指苗禮治截至昨日仍是13名終院非常任法官之一，任期到明年7月。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，終審法院首席法官馬道立前日罕有發出14頁聲明，反駁左報及建制派近月連番針對法院及部份法官攻擊，當中多次提及律政司的角色及功能。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n律政司：跟進法庭錯誤觀點<br />\n<br />\n律政司昨晚就馬道立聲明回覆本報查詢，未有直接回應針對法庭判決批評，僅指社會人士有權在法律容許範圍內就法庭裁決發表意見，但必須尊重司法獨立和法治精神，不應肆意抨擊司法人員，並引述《基本法》第63條，提及其職責包括主管刑事檢察工作，不受任何干涉；律政司司長則有憲制責任和職責，就刑事檢控工作作出決定及監督。<br />\n<br />\n回覆續又指，律政司與司法機構在刑事司法程序中的角色同樣重要，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"609166809af9a1d4ea11039c82de19687c646cec","tid":2216941,"uid":28651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"叫基本法賦予支那法官海外資格然後入終院揸旗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237a283214216b93ac54a043bedf725b2b7360a9","tid":2216941,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef24b43873e7e83a9bd84ee05bfae5b923c57e7","tid":2216941,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:53:41.000Z","msg":"Is that what CCP / Lam likes?"},{"pid":"7a0c8014c8b4081ec77b2ce35929f1d51262a2b5","tid":2216941,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZy5UUV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZy5UUV.jpg&h=1cc8d7e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"230203e64dd5fc58d49e3d58a510a7157c0c9789","tid":2216941,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"都冇法治<br />\n<br />\n人哋梗係唔做"},{"pid":"e7fe77013687e44d67f8dc8310cd63f0cc2edbdd","tid":2216941,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9ed9445c6aae761cf664e9adad1a3acec7b163","tid":2216941,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T06:01:26.000Z","msg":"港共: 可考慮引入海外中國法官填補空缺"},{"pid":"72be4306c5001a3f9c7535dd92de645c9a31e0b4","tid":2216941,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X6yd4hJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX6yd4hJ.jpg&h=8160d285&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bab46d406bbaf2dea7245f33759829c2fdb972e","tid":2216941,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:52:20.000Z","msg":"總辭係鬼"},{"pid":"b531bfaae882919d845269bc3e370afc47c46b66","tid":2216941,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:56:57.000Z","msg":"泛民總辭未"},{"pid":"44337b26cf1f1d1b937eff11cda0f035f8cc983e","tid":2216941,"uid":192052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609166809af9a1d4ea11039c82de19687c646cec","tid":2216941,"uid":28651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"叫基本法賦予支那法官海外資格然後入終院揸旗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:03:20.000Z","msg":"支那不嬲都海外<br />\n<br />\n大學都係"}]}